Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才提到说要初吻而已 结果她就跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还提初吻 你也太厚脸皮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果说自己是第一次\N那样的话印象不是会比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种谎话 人家光靠直觉就能看穿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而会是那种更让人不敢信任的典型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定，那时候的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第30话 「裸足的少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够烤成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生真是什么都会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃过再夸奖不是比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会烤蛋糕的男人很少见嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好，我是篠原若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会挑时间的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蛋糕是晓生先生做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用，不过味道不保证就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生真是什么都会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句话我刚才已经说过了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是请先吃吃看再夸奖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会烤蛋糕的男人很少见嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句刚才我也说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得你是故意漏我气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你说过\N晓生先生已经有未婚妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，喜欢的心情和那没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔？是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在谈什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 没有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那会是少女们的坏心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果一直这么死脑筋的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会连恋爱都谈不成的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是像个女孩子一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说是为了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这什么男生制服 可是一点都不好看的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，大家都说这样挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家说又怎样！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的关键是我这生活指导老师所决定的品味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算老师这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请教务主任也严正的说说她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不遵守校规的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子还是该穿着轻盈飘逸的裙子才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁决定的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这不是理事长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓、晓生先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！不，我是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教务主任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的国中部恳亲会让我也参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老早就想和理事长一起促膝长谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次提到有关…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去阿姆斯特丹姊妹校的视察团成员人选…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，也许最近遴选委员会就会发出正式的通知了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦请您让我的名字也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会记在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外，我有点事想找她谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把学生借给我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了…理事长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是他的容姿… 还是穿着打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，还有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太常以校规为理由去拘束学生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论如何…都请以尊重学生自主性的方式进行辅导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我谈的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小傻瓜，没有什么事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也是你那身威风凛凛装扮的迷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者，你面对那些啰唆的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然不改变自己信念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我感到有某种坚强与崇高…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长可以说那种话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我妹妹…不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，我在想什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家晓生先生已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉最近好像常看到这部车耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是今年的热门车款嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧－蒂－娜－
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，篠原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话请不要叫我篠原 叫我若叶就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人居然偷偷的一起出场 这可不太寻常喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成等下要约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然碰在一起罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，晓生先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去兜风呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像今天这样在这碰到 一定也是某种缘份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最近每天都跑来玩还敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜讬了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一辈子当作回忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就两个小时也可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会强迫人的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准！不准！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜不用跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为约会是指单独两个人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对，晓生先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔，请慢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好美的回忆喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海好漂亮… 风的感觉也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是最棒的约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想你应该也知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有未婚妻了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 难得人家正在陶醉的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是兜兜风而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是在吃醋吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这才不可能呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早啊，姬宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，欧蒂娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的明明是王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明只喜欢送我这枚戒指的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我会如此地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里会是这么的小鹿乱撞呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，你是怎么啦？ 居然会犯那种错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确…我到底是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗？欧蒂娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…抱歉，还让你照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是赶快去保健室冰敷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说姬宫啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，欧蒂娜大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，上车吧 去医院好好检查一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他事就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让姬宫也一起搭又有什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会是只能单独两个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你朋友告诉我的，不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先走了，安希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…晓生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让你陪我一起去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不都已经和家人一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼…是在明年春天对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是很好的人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是医生说今天还是不要走路比较好的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦！我还能走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要勉强的好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我背你吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生是花花公子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你很会讨女孩子欢心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…该说是… 不像理事长的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让人觉得是有点危险的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是不喜欢听从命令而穿着男生制服吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能是同类吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情形… 是因为王子的关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了想和从前就喜欢上的王子重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其背着走，还是用抱的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋鞋鞋鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快扔了那双鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我把重要的红鞋给…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是穿上的话 你会非跳舞跳到死不可的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道这样不行 却一样会去做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来，你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上也不拿着和我一样的红鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这，这个… 我只是拿着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会穿上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不穿还拿在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了！真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都拿着还不穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费的是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您肚子会饿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看您今天的晚餐 好像几乎都没吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有点没食欲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若叶那个家伙她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前若叶那个家伙说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说没有不能谈的恋爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢人的心情是无法自拔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是有不可以喜欢上的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我并不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也像若叶所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于喜欢的这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样有着连我自己都不知如何是好的部份在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子的吗？果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你也有喜欢的人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天上欧蒂娜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玻璃鞋的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一提…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也为她着迷是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决斗被打败时，我还大受打击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是因为被打败的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说居然有个少女动摇了我的信念…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子里还让我因此而思考着今后的生存方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有眼光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会成为好女人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是啊…理事长…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天好像没吃什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是身体不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我怎么了 这我该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难得，在这一大早…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这么早怎么逮的到你？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近比较忙的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙着看星星吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安，香苗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊，安希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道何时你才肯改口叫我嫂嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？你是…那个… 欧蒂娜同学对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃早餐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 倒是说…我母亲来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳母大人来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了，晓生先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岳母大人…真是难得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点话…想和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是什么事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作应该都很顺利的在进行的才是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是电话里头不方便谈的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生…\N最近你是不是在躲我的女儿 躲着香苗是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能接手这个学园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是和我女儿结婚后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别忘了婚约这种事 是随时都可以取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对香苗小姐一直都很体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至到若是发现彗星的话\N还想用她的名字命名的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闻，这是香苗喜欢的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都擦着她要我擦的香水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在只有两人的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长还康健吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种男人怎么样都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才是喔… 是我的王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说！听我说！欧蒂娜 我终于见到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生的未婚妻凤香苗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是个漂亮的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人长得美，头脑看起来也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上她还是个大小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这种人，的确会有小小的赢不了她的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的…可是王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫我记得你是AB型的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于让人摸不清楚\N又不大会吐露心事的类型是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 欧蒂娜大人是B型对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B型是…以自我为中心又非常爱钻牛角尖…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，真是不好意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来七实为什么会寄住到我们的房间来？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为七实也是B型的关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看来的确是非常爱钻牛角尖没错啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回　少女革命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「她的悲劇」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对命运默示录
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
